18:16.666 --> 18:19.461
And... And I'm a bit, um...

18:20.466 --> 18:22.625
Uh...

18:22.700 --> 18:24.631
Um, I'm just a bit...

18:24.700 --> 18:26.995
Inarticulate?

18:27.066 --> 18:29.125
Yes, that's it... I think.

18:29.201 --> 18:32.632
And you'd like to be the sort of person
who can use words like "inarticulate"?

18:32.700 --> 18:37.259
Yeah! I'd like to be able to talk to
Margaret and tell her how I feel.

18:37.335 --> 18:39.960
An intellectual who can get his
ideas across to the one he loves.

18:40.034 --> 18:42.001
Yes, that's it.
Easily done.

18:42.068 --> 18:45.001
Now then, you just stand
over here by the bird...

18:45.069 --> 18:47.728
put your right hand
on its left claw.

18:47.802 --> 18:50.235
Okay, lights out!

18:51.236 --> 18:53.463
Take this!
Ooh! Ooh!

18:53.536 --> 18:55.468
Am I gonna explode?

18:55.535 --> 18:58.263
No, no, it's quite safe. I just put it
there for a bit of visual excitement.

18:58.336 --> 19:01.063
It's not gonna hurt, is it?
Not a bit.

19:01.135 --> 19:03.126
Hold tight!

19:03.838 --> 19:05.632
The magic words:

19:05.704 --> 19:07.761
Julie Andrews.

19:07.837 --> 19:10.770
I could stand and
watch them for hours.

19:10.838 --> 19:12.827
They've such beautiful hands.
Mmm.

19:12.905 --> 19:15.336
Such fantastic delicacy, you see...

19:15.404 --> 19:20.666
but combined as well with this
almost preternatural strength.

19:20.738 --> 19:24.534
Doesn't it make you sad to see
animals caged up like this?

19:25.705 --> 19:27.638
Well, in a way, but, uh...

19:27.705 --> 19:30.640
quite honestly, they're really
no worse off than most of us.

19:30.708 --> 19:32.639
How do you mean?

19:32.707 --> 19:35.138
Well, metaphorically speaking...

19:35.206 --> 19:37.139
and in a very real sense...

19:37.207 --> 19:39.139
society creates its own cages.

19:39.207 --> 19:41.139
You know, cages of the mind.

19:41.207 --> 19:43.140
Yes. Yes.

19:43.208 --> 19:45.140
A curious kind of
cerebral captivity.

19:45.208 --> 19:47.139
Buy a flower, madam?

19:47.208 --> 19:50.731
Oh! Um, what's it for?
Depraved criminals.

19:50.808 --> 19:53.740
You see, civilization...

19:53.808 --> 19:56.470
has had the effect of...

19:56.543 --> 19:59.008
inhibiting our deepest...

19:59.077 --> 20:01.008
natural animal instincts, you see.

20:01.077 --> 20:03.009
Mmm.

20:03.077 --> 20:05.202
The conventions of an
ordered society...

20:05.277 --> 20:09.766
