20:15.077 --> 20:17.770
Oh, yes. One of the seminal forces.

20:17.843 --> 20:19.775
Um, as Rousseau said...

20:19.843 --> 20:22.277
we must learn to unlearn...

20:22.346 --> 20:27.277
