20:54.547 --> 20:56.980
Brahms! I can't believe it!

20:57.049 --> 20:58.980
You too?
Mmm.

20:59.049 --> 21:00.911
Ohh.

21:00.981 --> 21:02.913
Absolutely adore him.
Mmm.

21:02.981 --> 21:04.913
He has a...

21:04.981 --> 21:07.413
virile romanticism that
I find irresistible.

21:07.480 --> 21:10.915
Oh, Brahms is just so fantastic!

21:10.982 --> 21:12.914
Whenever I feel tense or anything...

21:12.982 --> 21:16.973
I put him on, just sprawl on the
carpet and let him flow all over me.

21:17.051 --> 21:19.812
- Would you like a little
taste of him now then?
