Goodness gracious.

22:30.390 --> 22:33.652
The French horn can sound
incredibly like a flute, you know.

22:33.724 --> 22:35.656
In fact, not many people notice...

22:35.723 --> 22:38.714
the flute-like qualities
of a French horn.

22:41.623 --> 22:44.056
