23:07.461 --> 23:10.394
Oh, that record was
new this morning.

23:14.461 --> 23:17.859
Where did you get
that fantastic thing?

23:17.928 --> 23:20.860
It is nice, isn't it?

23:20.928 --> 23:22.860
Oh, it's beautiful.

23:22.928 --> 23:25.862
Mmm. I got it off a stall, actually.

23:25.930 --> 23:29.362
Just saw it there
and had to have it.

23:29.428 --> 23:31.361
I'm rather like that, you know.

23:31.428 --> 23:33.361
I see something I want...

23:33.428 --> 23:35.361
and that's it, boy-o.

23:35.428 --> 23:37.362
Have to have it.
Me too.

23:37.429 --> 23:40.089
Yes, you too.

23:41.463 --> 23:43.395
Mmm.

23:43.463 --> 23:45.897
Have a look at it.
