23:45.964 --> 23:48.123
Oh!
Bit of a weight, isn't it?

23:48.198 --> 23:50.129
Oh, it's so smooth...

23:50.197 --> 23:52.131
and cool.

23:52.199 --> 23:54.426
Yes, that's the extraordinary
thing about marble.

23:54.498 --> 23:56.429
It's always 11 degrees cooler...

23:56.497 --> 23:58.430
than the air that surrounds it.

23:58.498 --> 24:00.430
Fahrenheit, of course.

24:02.765 --> 24:04.756
Do you like feeling things?

24:06.133 --> 24:09.360
Oh, yes,
I'm a very... tactile person.

24:09.432 --> 24:11.364
I love touching things.

24:11.433 --> 24:13.364
Sometimes...

24:13.433 --> 24:15.364
