24:22.035 --> 24:24.593
Y-You should try it.
Do it in here!

24:24.668 --> 24:27.293
Go on. Shut your eyes.

24:33.335 --> 24:35.323
Now feel something hard.

24:36.868 --> 24:38.801
Oh.

24:38.869 --> 24:40.801
