25:13.906 --> 25:15.838
Oh!
Mmm.

25:15.906 --> 25:17.839
Oh. It's delicious!

25:17.907 --> 25:19.838
Yeah?
Velvet.

25:19.907 --> 25:21.837
It's so wild.

25:21.906 --> 25:24.428
It really does something to me.

25:24.507 --> 25:26.803
Oh. Uh...
Hmm.

25:28.507 --> 25:31.735
