25:41.142 --> 25:43.131
Mmm.

25:44.576 --> 25:46.508
The freedom of it.

25:46.576 --> 25:49.007
The sun beating down.
Mmm.

25:49.076 --> 25:53.008
The incredible thing about the Italians
is the way they touch each other.

25:53.076 --> 25:55.633
Have you noticed that?
Yes. Cheers.

25:58.076 --> 26:01.439
