ahead and touch them.

26:07.511 --> 26:10.443
I mean, it's a healthy,
human thing to do.

26:10.511 --> 26:12.444
Y-You're so right.

26:12.512 --> 26:15.272
There's a tribe in... in Africa
who never say a word.

26:15.344 --> 26:18.106
They just touch each other.
That's how they communicate.

26:18.177 --> 26:20.110
Life is far too complicated.

26:20.177 --> 26:22.769
I think we should get
down to basic elements.

26:22.846 --> 26:24.539
Mmm.
I mean...

26:24.612 --> 26:28.476
For example, if you
were a girl, and I...

26:28.545 --> 26:31.604
I am a girl.
Well, of course!

26:35.380 --> 26:37.608
All right, but if...
if you were a girl...

26:37.680 --> 26:39.669
which, of course, you are...

26:41.247 --> 26:45.475
and if I were a man, which, for
argument's sake, let's say I am...

26:45.547 --> 26:49.036
and I wanted to touch you, well...

26:49.115 --> 26:51.047
I wouldn't feel restrained.

26:51.115 --> 26:53.047
