people waiting for?

27:48.854 --> 27:51.251
I want to live!
That's what matters... living.

27:51.320 --> 27:53.617
I want to do everything,
be everything...

27:53.688 --> 27:55.620
feel everything...

27:55.688 --> 27:57.619
Rape! Rape!

27:57.688 --> 27:59.552
No, no! Margaret! Margaret!

27:59.622 --> 28:02.053
