Yes.

29:02.959 --> 29:05.392
Well, this is a classic
double tempt situation.

29:05.460 --> 29:07.900
With a bit of luck, I can get
two sins for the price of one...

29:07.962 --> 29:10.860
spite from the perpetrating
pigeon and anger from the victim!

29:10.928 --> 29:12.360
It's terrific!

29:12.430 --> 29:14.861
