30:47.805 --> 30:49.736
no matter how stupid it is...

30:49.804 --> 30:51.736
that they're coming out with...

30:51.804 --> 30:54.846
till 10 minutes past 4:00
in the morning, you're in.

30:54.978 --> 30:57.944
