31:00.713 --> 31:03.577
Oh, that Margaret's such a...
gorgeous girl.

31:03.647 --> 31:05.135
Isn't she lovely?

31:05.213 --> 31:07.772
I'd like to know what
she's doing right now.

31:07.847 --> 31:10.506
