31:13.114 --> 31:15.046
Galileo's wonderful
little invention.

31:15.114 --> 31:17.102
Have you got sixpence?

31:18.514 --> 31:20.448
Yes.

31:20.515 --> 31:22.505
Have a peer through that.

31:24.315 --> 31:27.077
