think of us as their friends.

31:50.818 --> 31:52.751
I'm sure we all do, Inspector.

31:52.819 --> 31:55.251
Why don't you call me Reg?

31:55.318 --> 31:58.648
All right, Reg.
And you must call me Margaret.

31:58.718 --> 32:00.911
Here, she told him to
call her Margaret.

32:00.985 --> 32:04.417
