Oh, well. Julie Andrews.

33:14.626 --> 33:16.616
Randy!

33:17.693 --> 33:19.624
Afternoon, Seed.

33:19.692 --> 33:23.216
Hello, everybody. How are you, Peter?
Sorry I'm late, darling.

33:23.293 --> 33:25.225
Mmm! Hello, Randolph.
Hello.

33:25.293 --> 33:28.227
